WEBVTT

00:00:08.509 --> 00:00:15.682
<i>(Shino)</i>
<i>The Academy. In the past, this</i>
institute was the Hidden Leaf's
<i>training center for shinobi.</i>

00:00:15.716 --> 00:00:18.852
<i>Hopefuls underwent rigorous</i>
<i>training here.</i>

00:00:18.885 --> 00:00:23.557
However, the peace and stability
of our modern world has brought
<i>about big changes.</i>

00:00:23.590 --> 00:00:27.728
<i>Today, a general studies</i>
curriculum is offered alongside
<i>the ninjutsu program.</i>

00:00:27.761 --> 00:00:34.601
<i>The Academy's become a</i>
<i>scholastic facility where the</i>
next generation can explore many
<i>fields of study.</i>

00:00:41.141 --> 00:00:45.311
All right! This is gonna be the
place where I make my mark on
the world!

00:00:45.345 --> 00:00:50.617
Are you an idiot? You just got
done with a two‐week suspension
the Academy gave you, remember?!

00:00:50.651 --> 00:00:54.054
It's bad enough everyone's
gossiping about you.

00:00:54.087 --> 00:00:55.789
You should keep a low profile.

00:00:55.822 --> 00:00:59.359
Listen... what's done is done.
I can't go worrying about all
that.

00:00:59.392 --> 00:01:02.295
(Shikadai)
Hey, wait up!

00:01:05.031 --> 00:01:08.769
So, he didn't drop out... huh.

00:01:10.537 --> 00:01:20.514
♪♪

00:01:20.547 --> 00:01:30.557
♪♪

00:01:30.591 --> 00:01:40.534
♪♪

00:01:40.567 --> 00:01:50.577
♪♪

00:01:50.611 --> 00:02:00.554
♪♪

00:02:00.587 --> 00:02:10.597
♪♪

00:02:10.631 --> 00:02:20.607
♪♪

00:02:20.641 --> 00:02:30.651
♪♪

00:02:30.684 --> 00:02:37.157
♪♪

00:02:39.593 --> 00:02:48.569
♪♪

00:02:56.342 --> 00:03:00.547
Good morning, everybody!
My name's Boruto Uzumaki,
ya know!

00:03:00.581 --> 00:03:03.517
It's nice to meet all of you!

00:03:03.550 --> 00:03:07.053
Didn't I tell you to
keep a low profile?

00:03:07.087 --> 00:03:10.323
Hey, Denki. Which one's my desk?

00:03:10.356 --> 00:03:12.158
You can just sit anywhere.

00:03:12.192 --> 00:03:14.160
Oh, so that's how it works!

00:03:14.194 --> 00:03:17.698
Hey, you guys. How's it going?

00:03:17.731 --> 00:03:22.536
[classroom mutters]

00:03:22.569 --> 00:03:26.607
[sigh] This is so much better
than being stuck at home with
my Mom.

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:28.208
What? Your mom?

00:03:28.241 --> 00:03:32.145
(Boruto)
She forced me to study non stop
<i>for the whole last couple of</i>
<i>weeks.</i>

00:03:32.178 --> 00:03:35.549
[sigh]

00:03:35.582 --> 00:03:38.284
<i>(Ko Kogare)</i>
<i>How come he wasn't punished</i>
<i>after what he did?</i>

00:03:38.318 --> 00:03:40.654
I mean, he kinda was...

00:03:40.687 --> 00:03:42.556
But that wasn't just
some silly prank.

00:03:42.589 --> 00:03:46.593
If that train car had
landed in town, it would
have been a disaster.

00:03:46.627 --> 00:03:48.895
You saying that
there's a cover up?

00:03:48.929 --> 00:03:50.664
Shh! He can hear you.

00:03:53.199 --> 00:03:55.168
Oh! Uhh...

00:03:55.201 --> 00:03:56.903
Ignore them.

00:03:56.937 --> 00:04:01.041
Don't worry, I am. They
can say whatever they
want about me, I don't care!

00:04:01.074 --> 00:04:02.509
Well, okay then...

00:04:02.543 --> 00:04:06.079
[gasp] Look at that!
Forgot my textbook!

00:04:06.112 --> 00:04:08.348
Are you serious?
It's your first day!

00:04:08.381 --> 00:04:10.283
Hey! Share your book
with me, Shikadai.

00:04:10.316 --> 00:04:12.218
What a drag.
No way!

00:04:12.252 --> 00:04:14.287
Aw, c'mon now, don't
be like that!

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:17.724
Boruto sure stands
out in a crowd.

00:04:17.758 --> 00:04:24.097
Hm? But aren't people only
paying attention to him because
of that ridiculous stunt that
he pulled?

00:04:24.130 --> 00:04:28.234
You know him right?. Don't you
guys go way back, Sarada?

00:04:28.268 --> 00:04:30.771
Not really. Our parents
are friends, that's all.

00:04:30.804 --> 00:04:33.173
So, you're saying you're
childhood friends.

00:04:33.206 --> 00:04:36.843
No, I'd hardly say
that's what we are.

00:04:36.877 --> 00:04:40.046
In fact, I find it annoying even
<i>being associated with him.</i>

00:04:40.080 --> 00:04:44.751
Yeah, me, too... Although that
dad of his is seriously cool.

00:04:44.785 --> 00:04:46.920
Lord Naruto, the Hokage.

00:04:46.953 --> 00:04:49.890
Yeah!

00:04:49.923 --> 00:04:54.094
Difficult experiences in life
polish and refine a man!

00:04:54.127 --> 00:04:55.729
[small gasp]

00:04:55.762 --> 00:04:59.733
[sigh] ...riding on the
Hokage's coattails...

00:04:59.766 --> 00:05:02.803
Ahh! Hey, watch what
you're saying, Inojin!

00:05:05.906 --> 00:05:10.777
Uh, oh... Oops, did I
accidentally say that
out loud just now?

00:05:10.811 --> 00:05:12.378
[little groan]

00:05:12.412 --> 00:05:15.616
Hey, Inojin,
that's a bit harsh.

00:05:15.649 --> 00:05:19.419
Oh, sorry! If I offended,
I take it back.

00:05:19.452 --> 00:05:24.124
Although, you know that I'm only
saying what everybody else here
is thinking.

00:05:24.157 --> 00:05:29.730
If any other kid caused a train
to jump the tracks, chances are
they'd get thrown in jail.

00:05:29.763 --> 00:05:31.798
But that's...!

00:05:31.832 --> 00:05:37.270
Inojin, listen... you know that
isn't really what happened.

00:05:37.303 --> 00:05:40.140
I guess so.

00:05:40.173 --> 00:05:43.977
Anyway, Boruto, how
long's it been?

00:05:44.010 --> 00:05:45.846
Dunno. So, how ya doin'?

00:05:45.879 --> 00:05:47.313
Are you two friends?

00:05:47.347 --> 00:05:49.282
All of our parents are.

00:05:49.315 --> 00:05:51.251
I don't understand
you, Inojin...

00:05:51.284 --> 00:05:55.956
I know you've been like this for
a long time, but why do you
always shoot your mouth off?

00:05:55.989 --> 00:05:59.059
I'm really not trying to
cause trouble or anything.

00:05:59.092 --> 00:06:02.696
If he's telling the truth that
makes him look even worse!

00:06:02.729 --> 00:06:04.264
Yeah...

00:06:04.297 --> 00:06:07.333
Anyway, who our parents
are doesn't matter.

00:06:07.367 --> 00:06:09.402
We're friends, right?

00:06:11.104 --> 00:06:14.107
I just don't think you're
worthy of my trust.

00:06:14.140 --> 00:06:15.609
[gasp]

00:06:17.711 --> 00:06:21.214
Excuse me! We're going to be
studying together, so I believe
that all of us should just try
to get along!

00:06:21.247 --> 00:06:24.084
Spoken like a true Class Rep!

00:06:24.117 --> 00:06:25.318
[nervous gasp]

00:06:25.351 --> 00:06:28.454
[gasp] Everybody stand.

00:06:46.540 --> 00:06:49.109
Okay, Boruto. That's good.

00:06:49.142 --> 00:06:53.914
We're all done. We've now
measured everyone's basic skill
level.

00:06:53.947 --> 00:06:58.318
<i>Next time, we'll begin actual</i>
<i>practice using the data we've</i>
<i>gathered.</i>

00:06:58.351 --> 00:06:59.419
(all)
Right!

00:06:59.452 --> 00:07:02.388
Wow, Boruto! That
was really terrific!

00:07:02.422 --> 00:07:05.358
You had the second best
time in the whole class.

00:07:05.391 --> 00:07:09.563
Wait, what?! You mean
that I'm not on top?!

00:07:09.596 --> 00:07:12.933
All right, who's this
Iwabe that beat my time?

00:07:12.966 --> 00:07:15.736
Oh... I don't think he's
actually here today.

00:07:15.769 --> 00:07:20.974
He said something before about
it not being worth his time to
hang around with amateurs like
us.

00:07:21.007 --> 00:07:23.744
Really...?

00:07:25.011 --> 00:07:27.047
<i>[lunch chimes]</i>

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:29.516
Oh man, I'm starving!

00:07:30.316 --> 00:07:33.286
Oh! What's up, you guys?

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:35.021
Goin' to lunch? You
want some company?

00:07:35.055 --> 00:07:37.490
Sorry! We're just going
up to the rooftop.

00:07:37.524 --> 00:07:40.326
You know, you ought to
get going now, too.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:42.062
Yeah, see ya!

00:07:43.163 --> 00:07:45.231
What the heck is
their problem?

00:07:45.265 --> 00:07:47.601
Eh, whatever! Let's just go
get something to eat‐‐

00:07:47.634 --> 00:07:48.401
<i>(Iwabe)</i>
<i>Get outta here.</i>

00:07:48.434 --> 00:07:49.603
[gasps]

00:07:52.138 --> 00:07:54.841
You're bothering me.

00:07:54.875 --> 00:07:58.178
Can't you see I'm
using this room?

00:07:58.211 --> 00:07:59.379
Who's he?

00:07:59.412 --> 00:08:01.114
Iwabe Yuino.

00:08:01.147 --> 00:08:05.418
"Iwabe the Repeater". They say
that he failed the graduation
exams twice.

00:08:05.451 --> 00:08:08.288
Heh! So, an upperclassmen, huh?

00:08:08.321 --> 00:08:10.090
Cool! Nice to meetcha!

00:08:10.123 --> 00:08:13.660
I don't wanna be your little
friend. Hokage's boy.

00:08:13.694 --> 00:08:18.231
Hey, watch it; what does it
matter whose son I am?

00:08:18.264 --> 00:08:25.071
I just don't like the idea of
having a guy like you hanging
around me all the time.

00:08:25.105 --> 00:08:26.472
<i>...You got that?</i>

00:08:26.507 --> 00:08:28.008
[gasps]

00:08:28.041 --> 00:08:31.745
You think you're special? Go
hide in your father's shadow.

00:08:31.778 --> 00:08:33.446
Hey, you take that back!

00:08:33.479 --> 00:08:35.248
[groans]

00:08:35.281 --> 00:08:39.419
Seriously, that's it? You aren't
even worth my time...

00:08:39.452 --> 00:08:40.153
Boruto...!

00:08:40.186 --> 00:08:41.154
You dirty little...!

00:08:41.187 --> 00:08:44.290
If you have a problem
with me, bring it on!

00:08:44.324 --> 00:08:46.392
I wouldn't do it if I were you.

00:08:46.426 --> 00:08:51.464
I heard the instructors talking
about how impressed they all
were with Iwabe's taijutsu
skills.

00:08:51.497 --> 00:08:54.167
Oh yeah, then why does
he keep flunking?

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:57.538
I really don't know... but I
don't think you should test him.

00:08:57.571 --> 00:08:59.172
<i>[clang]</i>

00:08:59.205 --> 00:09:01.307
Listen to me! Strength is the
only thing that matters for a
ninja!

00:09:01.341 --> 00:09:06.279
What's the use of doing nothing
but simply studying obediently
like all of you?

00:09:06.312 --> 00:09:10.517
The current Hokage was the
strongest in all of history.

00:09:10.551 --> 00:09:14.354
As long as you're strong, a
ninja can get away with
anything!

00:09:14.387 --> 00:09:15.922
Aw, man, there he goes again.

00:09:15.956 --> 00:09:19.292
I know. At this point he
really should just drop
out of the Academy.

00:09:19.325 --> 00:09:25.532
But Iwabe, even Lord Seventh
made it his goal to use ninjutsu
in peaceful ways.

00:09:25.566 --> 00:09:27.400
That's why I also‐

00:09:27.433 --> 00:09:30.671
Just shut up! Weaklings
don't get to talk.

00:09:30.704 --> 00:09:34.407
Just ten years ago, our people
in were fighting in a war!

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:40.213
When Lord Hokage was a ninja on
the front lines, it wasn't like
<i>this at all.</i>

00:09:40.246 --> 00:09:44.417
But then, this place went soft
and turned into a school for
wimps!

00:09:44.450 --> 00:09:46.152
That's not gonna
fly with me!

00:09:46.186 --> 00:09:48.789
[gasp]

00:09:48.822 --> 00:09:54.928
A weakling who got accepted here
only by riding on his old man's
<i>coattails... is nothing more</i>
<i>than an embarrassment!</i>

00:09:54.961 --> 00:09:55.929
[gasp]

00:09:57.631 --> 00:10:00.433
He's nothing like that at all.

00:10:00.466 --> 00:10:01.668
Huh?

00:10:01.702 --> 00:10:04.337
You're wrong! Boruto's
not like that at all!

00:10:04.370 --> 00:10:07.608
It was 'cause of watching Boruto
that I wanted to join the
Academy.

00:10:07.641 --> 00:10:09.843
You don't know anything!

00:10:09.876 --> 00:10:11.344
[gasps]

00:10:11.377 --> 00:10:13.179
Some brave words you got
there...

00:10:13.213 --> 00:10:18.484
But still... you only get to
speak to me like that after
you defeat me!

00:10:18.519 --> 00:10:20.721
Cut it out!

00:10:21.588 --> 00:10:23.657
[grunt]

00:10:23.690 --> 00:10:28.695
I see... So your idea of
strength is just to bully people
into doing what you want, is
that it?

00:10:28.729 --> 00:10:30.731
What did you say?!

00:10:32.198 --> 00:10:33.567
Boruto...!

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:36.069
It's okay, Shikadai!

00:10:36.102 --> 00:10:40.073
Before I came here, I made a
decision that I wouldn't fight.

00:10:40.106 --> 00:10:43.176
But if I have to...
I'll take you on!

00:10:43.209 --> 00:10:46.880
Heh. Interesting.

00:10:49.282 --> 00:10:50.050
[nervous gasp]

00:10:50.083 --> 00:10:52.018
Hm.

00:10:57.558 --> 00:11:01.294
(Anko)
Oh! Hello there, Shino Sensei!

00:11:01.327 --> 00:11:04.497
So, today's the day that Boruto
starts, isn't it?

00:11:04.531 --> 00:11:06.099
That's right.

00:11:06.132 --> 00:11:10.303
To be suspended on the first day
of school! He's quite a
character.

00:11:10.336 --> 00:11:14.407
I never expected that I'd be
assigned to be his homeroom
teacher....

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:16.076
Well, better make
the most of it!

00:11:16.109 --> 00:11:19.680
Oh, yes, don't worry, I'm going
to be very strict with him.

00:11:19.713 --> 00:11:22.448
That's my job and my
responsibility now.

00:11:22.482 --> 00:11:23.984
'Scuse me.

00:11:28.221 --> 00:11:29.590
(Shino)
What!?

00:11:29.623 --> 00:11:29.856
[gasp]

00:11:31.157 --> 00:11:32.826
Oh my...

00:11:32.859 --> 00:11:36.229
Where are my students...?!

00:11:42.068 --> 00:11:46.106
[groan] What do we do?
And what about class?!

00:11:46.139 --> 00:11:49.209
Eh, so what? We can just blame
the guys who are fighting.

00:11:49.242 --> 00:11:50.577
This is so annoying!

00:11:50.611 --> 00:11:53.714
[excited chatter]

00:11:53.747 --> 00:11:56.349
What's the matter? Not
getting scared, are you?

00:11:56.382 --> 00:12:01.555
Ha! No way! This exercise hall
is like a fighting ring!

00:12:01.588 --> 00:12:03.590
This is gonna be fun!

00:12:03.624 --> 00:12:07.360
Watch closely, you guys!

00:12:07.393 --> 00:12:11.264
This is a ninjutsu match,
and we'll be following
Academy rules!

00:12:11.297 --> 00:12:14.735
So don't worry. I won't
be using my weapon.

00:12:14.768 --> 00:12:18.138
Because if I did use it,
then you'd be dead.

00:12:18.171 --> 00:12:19.773
Hm!

00:12:20.641 --> 00:12:22.776
This whole thing is my fault!

00:12:22.809 --> 00:12:24.578
<i>(Shikadai)</i>
<i>No, it isn't.</i>

00:12:24.611 --> 00:12:28.715
He brought it all upon himself
by taking up this challenge.

00:12:28.749 --> 00:12:30.851
He's gonna get suspended again.

00:12:30.884 --> 00:12:34.154
You think that's all he'll get?

00:12:34.187 --> 00:12:35.989
I say expelled.

00:12:36.022 --> 00:12:37.123
Huh!?

00:12:37.157 --> 00:12:39.526
But I suppose at least
he's not a coward.

00:12:39.560 --> 00:12:41.394
He's just stupid.

00:12:41.427 --> 00:12:44.164
[gasp]

00:12:45.632 --> 00:12:47.133
[grunts]

00:12:47.734 --> 00:12:50.804
[attack grunts]

00:12:54.074 --> 00:12:56.109
Oh! So you can keep
up a little, huh?

00:12:57.177 --> 00:12:59.112
[grunt]

00:13:01.848 --> 00:13:03.049
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>He's fast...</i>

00:13:03.083 --> 00:13:06.687
[grunts]

00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:08.722
Well, that's not gonna work!

00:13:08.755 --> 00:13:13.159
[attack yell]

00:13:13.193 --> 00:13:15.762
[grunt]

00:13:15.796 --> 00:13:17.263
Oh, no...!

00:13:18.498 --> 00:13:20.834
[cough]

00:13:20.867 --> 00:13:23.537
What's the matter?
You done already?

00:13:23.570 --> 00:13:28.742
[heavy breathing]

00:13:28.775 --> 00:13:33.179
Dammit. You made me get my
clothes all dirty.

00:13:33.213 --> 00:13:36.082
[crowd murmurs]

00:13:36.116 --> 00:13:38.819
I thought you weren't
interested in this?

00:13:38.852 --> 00:13:41.788
[gasp] I'm not!

00:13:41.822 --> 00:13:44.825
It sure doesn't look like
you're not interested.

00:13:44.858 --> 00:13:47.193
You're delusional.

00:13:47.227 --> 00:13:51.998
Anyway, I think he's
in real trouble. He's no
match for that guy.

00:13:55.902 --> 00:13:56.436
[clanging]

00:13:58.872 --> 00:14:00.206
Pretty clever...

00:14:05.712 --> 00:14:07.681
[grunt]

00:14:07.714 --> 00:14:09.683
[grunts]

00:14:09.716 --> 00:14:11.217
Hands off!

00:14:11.652 --> 00:14:13.987
It's over!

00:14:16.156 --> 00:14:16.489
[gasp]

00:14:16.957 --> 00:14:19.459
I'm over here!

00:14:19.492 --> 00:14:19.526
[grunts]

00:14:22.262 --> 00:14:23.564
Huh!?

00:14:24.965 --> 00:14:27.467
[gasps]
A substitution?!

00:14:27.500 --> 00:14:28.168
Damn it!

00:14:33.840 --> 00:14:34.440
[groan] Where...?

00:14:39.513 --> 00:14:40.113
Behind you!

00:14:40.146 --> 00:14:40.847
[gasp]

00:14:40.881 --> 00:14:45.619
[struggling grunts]

00:14:47.287 --> 00:14:51.892
Substitution with a Disguise
Jutsu, huh? That's pretty good!

00:14:51.925 --> 00:14:54.895
Yeah, you too. Shadow Clones.

00:14:54.928 --> 00:14:58.732
And they even stay manifested.
That's some chakra.

00:14:58.765 --> 00:15:02.168
What's Chakra?

00:15:02.202 --> 00:15:08.575
"The energy that's produced by
the immeasurable quantity of
cells that are contained within
the human body"

00:15:08.609 --> 00:15:13.514
Yeah. Learning how to manipulate
chakra is the first step toward
mastering ninjutsu.

00:15:16.517 --> 00:15:19.786
Interesting! But I can take on
any number of clones!

00:15:19.820 --> 00:15:21.054
We'll see!

00:15:23.924 --> 00:15:24.658
Too easy!

00:15:24.691 --> 00:15:26.392
[grunts]

00:15:26.793 --> 00:15:28.461
[attack grunt]

00:15:29.295 --> 00:15:31.532
[shouting]

00:15:33.867 --> 00:15:35.802
[exhausted grunt]

00:15:35.836 --> 00:15:39.973
You know, you really shouldn't
waste your clones, or you'll
run out of energy too fast.

00:15:40.006 --> 00:15:43.276
Just shut up!

00:15:43.309 --> 00:15:44.210
Heh.

00:15:47.380 --> 00:15:49.750
It's clear that guy's
used to combat.

00:15:49.783 --> 00:15:54.621
The data says he was
the top student in
ninjutsu last year, too.

00:15:54.655 --> 00:15:59.092
Although it seems his grades in
the other courses were dismal.

00:15:59.125 --> 00:16:01.695
Man, this guy is a serious drag.

00:16:01.728 --> 00:16:04.497
The Academy should've just let
him graduate already!

00:16:06.967 --> 00:16:11.337
Wait! There! Get him!

00:16:11.371 --> 00:16:13.473
