unless I pass courses that have
absolutely nothing to do with
ninjutsu, then I'm stuck here!

00:17:21.642 --> 00:17:26.146
You think... maybe you might
just be really bad at studying?

00:17:26.179 --> 00:17:29.215
[grunt] And so what
if I am, huh?!

00:17:29.249 --> 00:17:32.052
